  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9\u0da7 \u0d85\u0daf \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dbb 75,000 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "75,000 gas cylinders distributed to Colombo today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "75,000 gas cylinders were distributed to the Colombo area today (12), Litro Gas Company's media spokesperson V. Mr. Keteswaram said this afternoon.",
        "He also mentioned that most of the gas was distributed to the apartments in Naraga, Colombo. He further said that gas distribution to outlying provinces will start tomorrow (13).",
        "Long litro gas queues could be seen yesterday in and around Colombo and people were kept in queues for gas cylinders for over a month."
      ],
